🚀 How to Run the Project
1️⃣ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/patient-vital-monitoring.git
cd patient-vital-monitoring
2️⃣ Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
3️⃣ Configure Environment Variables

Create a .env file:

GCP_PROJECT=your_project_id
PUBSUB_SUBSCRIPTION=projects/your_project/subscriptions/patient_vitals_subscription
BRONZE_PATH=gs://bucket/bronze/
SILVER_PATH=gs://bucket/silver/
BIGQUERY_TABLE=project.dataset.table
TEMP_LOCATION=gs://bucket/temp/
STAGING_LOCATION=gs://bucket/staging/
REGION=us-central1
4️⃣ Run Patient Simulator
python simulator/patient_vitals_simulator.py
5️⃣ Deploy Streaming Dataflow Pipeline
python dataflow/streaming_medallion_pipeline.py
